author: Nexcell Pride
text:
Wow, a wonderful stream. :_ちょうちょ:
Too many time passed for returning to Fall Guys.
Also, Rushia did her best and doesn't got altered like August 2020 and first gameplay at September 2020.
At second stream at September 2020 and October 2020 she was almost peaceful like today. Really surprising, because at October 2020 she said about leaving FallGuys, presumably due to her health condition about raging.

But well, she's very known at raging, but every follower and fan may know about avoid that status and reach her charismatic side... Remembering that 3D debut at 2019 November 30th and later starting at 2020 September 6th when she started to being closer to audience... 
Also demonstrated at today's Supaachaato Orei Time :_ハート:
